      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>GAYER-John. Of Brookville, New York, on August 20, 2000. Beloved husband of Pauline, loving father of Helen Shettell, proud grandfather of Brandon, dear brother of Wanda Mallon, also survived by son-in-law, Norman. Visitation Dodge Thomas Funeral Home, Glen Cove, Tuesday 3-5 and 7-9. Service Brookville Reformed Church, Wednesday 11 A.M.</p>
